title: Macquarie St Food Store
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small cafe with a mostly vegetarian menu, with a few vegan options clearly marked. The daily soup is usually vegan. Try the veggie burger. Busy at times so wait might be long. Reservations taken, and take away available.
